Class Results

  • java.lang.Object
    • ninja.Results

  • public class Results
extends Object
    Convenience methods for the generation of Results. {@link Results#forbidden() generates a results and sets it to forbidden. A range of shortcuts are available from here.
    Author:
    rbauer
